data.description: Welcome to your dream home at 6004 Duren Meadows Drive, Lithonia, GA 30058! This impressive 5 bedroom, 3 bathroom residence offers a perfect blend of luxury and functionality. Step inside to discover a bonus room on the main level, complete with an attached full bathroom, providing versatility for guests, a home office, or a playroom. Fresh paint and new carpeting create a contemporary feel, while a brand-new roof ensures worry-free living for years to come. Vaulted ceilings add a touch of grandeur to the spacious living areas, complemented by both front and rear entrance staircases for convenience and style. Cozy up by the fireplace on chilly evenings, adding warmth and charm to your home. Relax and entertain on the nice back deck, perfect for enjoying the serene surroundings. The expansive driveway leads to a two-car garage, offering ample parking space. No HOA means the freedom to customize and enjoy your property without restrictions.  Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this exceptional property yours!
